title: Helsesista
overview: Tale Maria Krohn Engvik is the public health nurse who decided to reach out more widely to young people by communicating with them in their own arena. With a mix of serious knowledge, humor and personality, she reaches up to 150,000 viewers on Snapchat daily. Now she has created a TV series for and with young people where difficult and taboo topics such as sex, the body, nude images, suicidal thoughts and heartbreak are addressed in a simple and harmless way.
